<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->

# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
Generate a binary string then loop over string to find distance between two 1's and then store the max distance in a variable

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->O(N)
where N=length of Binary String

- Space complexity:
<!-- Add your space complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
