**`builtin_ctz` — `gcc` builtin function that counts the number of trailing zeroes**
```
int binaryGap(int n)
{
	int out{0};
	for(auto i{32}; n; n&=n-1)
	{
		out = max(out, __builtin_ctz(n)-i);
		i   = __builtin_ctz(n);
	}
	return out;
}
```
